{"type":"item.completed","item":{"id":"item_93","type":"agent_message","text":"# Implementation Notes\n\n## Decisions Made\n- Added shared backend-selection types in [`src/shared/domain.rs`](/root/new-ralph-burning/ralph-burning-rewrite/src/shared/domain.rs): `BackendFamily`, `BackendSpec`, `ModelSpec`, `ResolvedBackendTarget`, `BackendRole`, and `SessionPolicy`.\n- Implemented the execution facade in [`src/contexts/agent_execution/model.rs`](/root/new-ralph-burning/ralph-burning-rewrite/src/contexts/agent_execution/model.rs), [`src/contexts/agent_execution/service.rs`](/root/new-ralph-burning/ralph-burning-rewrite/src/contexts/agent_execution/service.rs), and [`src/contexts/agent_execution/session.rs`](/root/new-ralph-burning/ralph-burning-rewrite/src/contexts/agent_execution/session.rs), including resolver precedence, timeout/cancellation handling, failure-class mapping, raw-output preservation, and session reuse.\n- Added filesystem-backed raw-output/session persistence in [`src/adapters/fs.rs`](/root/new-ralph-burning/ralph-burning-rewrite/src/adapters/fs.rs) and a deterministic [`src/adapters/stub_backend.rs`](/root/new-ralph-burning/ralph-burning-rewrite/src/adapters/stub_backend.rs).\n- Added a CLI construction hook in [`src/cli/run.rs`](/root/new-ralph-burning/ralph-burning-rewrite/src/cli/run.rs) so the service is constructible from current adapter wiring ahead of `run start`.\n\n## Spec Deviations\n- `AgentExecutionPort::invoke` returns an `InvocationEnvelope` with inline raw output first, and `AgentExecutionService` rewrites that to a stored `runtime/backend/*` reference after persistence. This preserves the requested trait shape while keeping persistence/normalization in the service layer.\n\n## Testing\n- Added service tests in [`tests/unit/agent_execution_test.rs`](/root/new-ralph-burning/ralph-burning-rewrite/tests/unit/agent_execution_test.rs) for precedence, capability/availability failures, transport/schema/domain mapping, timeout, cancellation, envelope construction, and session policy enforcement.\n- Added adapter contract tests in [`tests/unit/stub_backend_test.rs`](/root/new-ralph-burning/ralph-burning-rewrite/tests/unit/stub_backend_test.rs).\n- Ran `nix develop --command bash -lc 'cargo fmt --all && cargo test && cargo clippy --all-targets --all-features -- -D warnings'`.\n\n---"}}
